  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2 15\u0d9a \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "15 crores worth of gold is about to be taken out of the airport",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Katunayake airport security says that an employee of the duty-free shopping mall was arrested for trying to leave Katunayake airport with 60 gold biscuits worth 15 million and seventy lakh rupees hidden in his waist.",
        "These golden biscuits weighing 06 kg and 995 grams were prepared into 06 parcels and hidden in the waist area while being taken out of the airport, they were arrested by a group of Katunayake airport security personnel.",
        "Later, this person and the stock of gold biscuits he was carrying have been handed over to the airport customs officials for further investigation.",
        "Customs officials suspect that these gold biscuits may have been brought from Dubai to Katunayake airport, and it has been revealed in the preliminary investigations conducted by the customs that he had arranged for this stock of gold biscuits to be taken out of the airport."
      ],
